.TH DADD 1 "2026-01-02" "dumbass-tree" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
dadd \- safer dd wrapper (write images to USB with guard rails)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B dadd
[--dry-run] [-v] <command>
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B write <image> <device>
Write image to block device with 1- or 2-tier confirmation.
.TP
.B fatimg create <path> [--size 8G]
Create a file-backed FAT filesystem image.
